text: I’m deeply saddened by the passing of the Rev. Billy Graham, a very cherished Christian leader and an exemplary North Carolinian.  There is no doubt he was called by God, and he heeded that call as well — if not better — than anyone else ever has.

The #schumershutdown means nearly 100,000 national guardsmen will be sent home from training.  It means that Pilot Training and other training programs will be cancelled harming our readiness and putting operations in severe jeopardy.
